Beating Canada at home will help , he said in an interview.Some Canadian fans were bitter that Canadian-born Brett Hull , the son of hockey legend Bobby Hull , scored twice in Saturday 's game -- for the United States.Hull , who has dual citizenship , played most of the game to chants of Brett Hull sucks from the partisan crowd in Montreal 's Molson Centre.I think he should have played for Canada .
